quran[9{c,v,t}:
11,63,"saleh ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, tum ne kuch is baat par bhi ghhor kya ke agar mein apne rab ki taraf se aik saaf shahadat rakhta tha, aur phir is ne apni rehmat se bhi mujh ko Nawaz diya to iss ke baad Allah ki pakar se mujhe kon bachaaye ga agar mein uss ki nafarmani karoon? tum mere kis kaam aa satke ho siwaye is ke ke mujhe aur ziyada khasaray mein daal do"
11,64,"aur ae meri qoum ke logo, dekho yeh Allah ki oontni tumahray liye aik nishani hai isay khuda ki zameen mein charnay ke liye azad chore do iss se zara tarruz nah karna warna kuch ziyada der nah guzray gi ke tum par khuda ka azaab aa jaye ga """
11,65,"magar unhon ne oontni ko maar dala is par saleh ne unn ko khabardaar kar diya ke"" bas ab teen din apne gharon mein aur reh bas lau yeh aisi meyaad hai jo jhooti nah saabit hogi """
11,66,aakhir-kaar jab hamaray faislay ka waqt aa gaya to hum ne apni rehmat se saleh ko aur unn logon ko jo is ke sath imaan laaye thay bacha liya aur uss din ki ruswai se un ko mehfooz rakha be shak tera rab hi darasal taaqatwar aur baala dast hai
11,67,rahay woh log jinhon ne zulm kya tha to aik sakht dhamakay ne un ko dhar liya aur woh apni bustiyon mein is terhan be hiss o harkat parre ke parre reh gay
11,68,ke goya woh wahan kabhi basey hi nah thay suno! smod ne apne rab se kufar kya suno! daur pheink diye gay smod !
11,69,"aur dekho, ibrahim ke paas hamaray farishtay khushkhabri liye hue puhanche kaha tum par salam ho ibrahim ne jawab diya tum par bhi salam ho phir kuch der nah guzri ke ibrahim aik bhana howa bitchrha ( un ki ziyafat ke liye ) le aaya"
11,70,"magar jab dekha ke un ke haath khanay par nahi barhatay to woh un se mushtaba ho gaya aur dil mein un se khauf mehsoos karne laga onhon ne kaha"" daro nahi, hum to loot ki qoum ki taraf beje gay hain """
11,71,ibrahim ki biwi bhi khari hui thi woh yeh sun kar hans di phir hum ne is ko ishaq ki aur ishaq ke baad Yaqoob ki khushkhabri di
